OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThere will
OL,6,Fbe a mixture of clear spells and
OL,7,Fscattered showers this evening. The
OL,8,Fshowers will become more confined to
OL,9,Fthe northwest overnight. A widespread
OL,10,Ffrost forming, with icy patches.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FAfter a cold start, there
OL,13,Fwill be sunny spells and further
OL,14,Fshowers on Saturday. Most of the
OL,15,Fshowers are likely in the northwest.
OL,16,FLighter winds overall, and feeling
OL,17,Fless chilly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
